{
  "stem": "1975.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 69.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So you never-- it was like a lottery.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You didn't know who was genuine, and who is going-- just going to take the money and then take the life of the child.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we decided through some way-- and by cutting down the ghetto, by shrinking, there were a number of houses which were left outside of the ghetto, within the perimeter of the general surroundings, but it was not-- they didn't watch that so much.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because that was actually considered outside, because it used to be the ghetto, but then they deleted this part.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then they put a fence, and still the fence remains over this circle around.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But still, we had-- the real ghetto was a little bit farther, about 600, 700 meters farther.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So what we decided, when we went to work, that one of us will bribe the guard.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were some guards who you were able to bribe them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And didn't need too much money for doing that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We gave them some certain things.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we used to bring in-- when we used to come from the city-- we bring in some-- we concentrated on getting some sugar, getting water and bread.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "This was the three items that you can survive with.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we brought it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In one of these abandoned houses, we used to, every time, to come in and to leave certain things.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then we used to go to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then, one day, we were actually five people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was my aunt's nephew, who was like 30 years old.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a older man by the name of Shayka Fin, Fin was his last name, who was working together-- his uncle was working to the ghetto with my uncle in the supply of the bread.",
      "word_count": 36
    }
  ],
